column5: Heavy rains today and tomorrow be careful on the streams etc. Keep a special eye on the kids.

Yeah, we got over 5 centimeters of rain from Tuesday night to this morning... and I thought what the heck, my good Canadian friends like to share their cold air masses with us so well... let's send them some rain!We currently have strong gusty winds and I'll be sending those up there as well. Enjoy!
CLOCA has issued a flood warning for the creeks in durham...all of you steelheaders be safe
